g.title: j2784565195
g.text: Tell me of this terrible god you have unleashed
Your Xipe Totec, your flayed god

g.title: j3741140846
g.text: You think but you do not know
But yet you think its an enemy ¿Por qué?

g.title: j3956393443
g.text: You treat him like an enemy though
If you do not know what he is after

g.title: j2908673272
g.text: This void creature that sacrifices others and wears their skin like ancient flayed god of old, Xipe Totec

g.title: j695378016
g.text: That THING decided it'd be a fun experiment to turn the parents on the Zariman against their children -

g.title: j1010163748
g.text: All it does is leave death and destruction in its wake. No matter what it's motivations are, it doesn't matter. Trust me.

g.title: j2558730502
g.text: And then gave the children magical void powers so they could murder their own parents so it could LEARN from the slaughter.

g.title: j3580735548
g.text: Trust you to understand the mind of a god
Don't care how old you are

g.title: j1670874297
g.text: It's had an opportunity to learn from love, from sacrifice, from kindness. But it seems to CHOOSE to seek out chaos and murder.

g.title: j3504484090
g.text: Even if it's just a toddler smashing toys together to understand the world around it, we're those toys. It has to be stopped.

g.title: j3315808247
g.text: I'll continue to hold out hope it isn't an enemy, but... it's not giving me a lot of reasons to think it isn't.

g.title: j2533293861
g.text: I refuse to believe it's benign after all I've seen. After all it's done to me.

g.title: j101116871
g.text: You are not a god babas
Don't pretend you think like one
Otherwise you are no better than that Entrati cabrón

g.title: j3249620805
g.text: And you think you can stop a god

g.title: j3312337858
g.text: You are not a god babas
Don't pretend you think like one
Otherwise you are no better than those orokin cabrones

g.title: j1091979299
g.text: You are not a god babas
Don't pretend you think like one

g.title: j2306747052
g.text: No clue. I tend to make this shit up as I go. lol

g.title: j2681185440
g.text: I think I can try. Like I did here. And that's all any of us can do.

g.title: j2664250577
g.text: It's up to others, now. My place is here in 1999 with all of you.

g.title: j68258164
g.text: The moment they ring you will go running
You are a drifter, a soldier, you will go to save the future when they need you

g.title: j3871550158
g.text: Seems to work for you, so I won't judge

g.title: j45653418
g.text: All we can ask for I suppose

g.title: j3009230655
g.text: Do not lie to me or tell me you'll take me for walks, babas
Someday you will escape and never come back

g.title: j1316109379
g.text: Faith in what does not matter I suppose
As long as it gets you through
